@startuml
title Prototype C - Log Store Pipeline + Async Enrichment

skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Monospaced

actor "Producers" as Prod

rectangle "Watcher Service (Go)\n- validate\n- normalize\n- store raw\n- publish pointer" as Watcher
cloud "Log Store\n(OpenSearch/S3/ELK)" as LogStore
queue "Kafka\n(pointer events)" as Broker
rectangle "Core Service (Spring)\n- consume pointers\n- rules\n- tickets" as Core
rectangle "NLP Service (FastAPI)\n- consume pointers\n- fetch raw\n- enrich" as NLP
database "PostgreSQL" as PG

Prod --> Watcher : POST /api/v1/ingest
Watcher --> LogStore : write raw event\n(body, headers)
Watcher --> Broker : publish PointerEvent\n(event_id, location)

Broker --> Core : consume PointerEvent
Core --> PG : insert/update ticket\n(minimal fields)

Broker --> NLP : consume PointerEvent
NLP --> LogStore : fetch raw text
NLP --> LogStore : write enrichment\n(category, severity, entities)
NLP --> Broker : publish EnrichmentEvent\n(event_id, summary)

Broker --> Core : consume EnrichmentEvent
Core --> PG : attach enrichment

Core ..> NLP : gRPC Analyze\n(on-demand re-enrich/backfill)

@enduml
